<div1 type="trialAccount" id="t17540116-27">
               <interp inst="t17540116-27" type="collection" value="BAILEY"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17540116-27" type="year" value="1754"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17540116-27" type="uri" value="sessionsPapers/17540116"></interp>
               <interp inst="t17540116-27" type="date" value="17540116"></interp>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17540116-27-off146-c203" targOrder="Y" targets="t17540116-27-defend250 t17540116-27-off146 t17540116-27-verdict148"></join>
               <join result="criminalCharge" id="t17540116-27-off146-c204" targOrder="Y" targets="t17540116-27-defend252 t17540116-27-off146 t17540116-27-verdict148"></join>
         
               <p>112, 113. (M.) 
               
                  <persName id="t17540116-27-defend250" type="defendantName">
                     Anne 
                     Purvise 
                  <interp inst="t17540116-27-defend250" type="surname" value="Purvise"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-defend250" type="given" value="Anne"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-defend250" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , <rs id="t17540116-27-deflabel144" type="occupation">widow</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17540116-27-defend250 t17540116-27-deflabel144"></join>, and 
               
                  <persName id="t17540116-27-defend252" type="defendantName">
                     Frances 
                     Hayes 
                  <interp inst="t17540116-27-defend252" type="surname" value="Hayes"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-defend252" type="given" value="Frances"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-defend252" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
            , <rs id="t17540116-27-deflabel145" type="occupation">spinster</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17540116-27-defend252 t17540116-27-deflabel145"></join>, were indicted for <rs id="t17540116-27-off146" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-off146" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-off146" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing one pair of linen sheets, value 2 s. 6 d.
            </rs> the goods of 
               
                  <persName id="t17540116-27-victim254" type="victimName">
                     George 
                     Carlow 
                  <interp inst="t17540116-27-victim254" type="surname" value="Carlow"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-victim254" type="given" value="George"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-victim254" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t17540116-27-off146 t17540116-27-victim254"></join>
                  </persName>
                
            , <rs id="t17540116-27-cd147" type="crimeDate">January 3</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17540116-27-off146 t17540116-27-cd147"></join>. || .</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17540116-27-person255">
                  Elizabeth 
                  Carlow 
               <interp inst="t17540116-27-person255" type="surname" value="Carlow"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-person255" type="given" value="Elizabeth"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-person255" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . One of the prisoners I employed in my house, the other I took in for a day or two, knowing her mother. I missed the pair of sheets, and immediately suspected the prisoners. Hays told me one was sold, and the other pawned The other owned to nothing.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17540116-27-person256">
                  Deborah 
                  Tomison 
               <interp inst="t17540116-27-person256" type="surname" value="Tomison"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-person256" type="given" value="Deborah"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-person256" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I bought one of the sheets of Purvise.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17540116-27-person257">
                  Robert 
                  Pratt 
               <interp inst="t17540116-27-person257" type="surname" value="Pratt"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-person257" type="given" value="Robert"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-person257" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am a pawnbroker. Hayes brought the other sheet, and pawned it with me for twenty pence.</p>
               <p>[Both produced in Court, and deposed to by the prosecutrix.]</p>
               <p>Purvise's Defence.</p>
               <p>I am guilty of taking one, and not the other.</p>
               <p>Hayes's Defence.</p>
               <p>I do not know what to say.</p>
               <p>Both <rs id="t17540116-27-verdict148" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-verdict148" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-verdict148" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder1s"></interp>
               guilty, 10 d.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17540116-27-punish149" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17540116-27-punish149" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17540116-27-defend250 t17540116-27-punish149"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17540116-27-defend252 t17540116-27-punish149"></join>
               
                     <note>[Transportation. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
            </div1>
